  "subject": "[BUG] Increase connection pool for NCMP RestTemplate",
  "commit_message": "[BUG] Increase connection pool for NCMP RestTemplate\n\nPresently NCMP is limited to 5 parallel connections to DMI.\nThis is causing a performance degradation when making parallel\nrequests to NCMP, especially with long DMI response time (1 second).\nThis addresses the issue by increasing pool size to 50 per DMI host.\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-1968\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\nChange-Id: I88fb313c3ee773ef1382ec6222df4f46d1a88324\n",
